How to visit the website?
1. Please changd your directory to the directory where manage.py is.
2. Open terminal and run $ python manage.py syncdb 
2. $ python manage.py runserver
3. The website will be deployed to localhost:8000/nbamatch

note: you may be asked to create a superuser for admin page.
      If you cannot view any posted news in home page, you may need to create news posts on your own since the website is deployed locally.

Implement Environment:
Ubuntu: 14.04
Django: 1.6
Python: 2.7
Database: SQLite3